{"tid":1219651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歡迎Collaborate] 狗狗濫權罪行合集","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T16:27:02.000Z","uid":28914,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"762dca0c8cf9e668c9cdf8a0087abc9fc9e0f764","tid":1219651,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:15:22.000Z","msg":"承接住格離POST嘅第二波攻勢，話說小弟同朋友整合緊呢幾日班狗係全港各地做嘅痴線嘢，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴力毆打示威者，喵住示威者個頭headshot，恐嚇記者</span></strong></span>，一一都會記錄！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我地會將呢啲片段，加埋各種語言嘅caption寄去全球各大傳媒，放上唔同社交媒體，尤其係Twitter，亦會向聯合國人權高級專員辦事處舉報，指證香港黑警違反國際人權公約！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下就係條link，歡迎各位巴絲踴躍投稿！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://ethercalc.org/elabpolice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fethercalc.org%2Felabpolice&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=5b30b07e\" target=\"_blank\">https://ethercalc.org/elabpolice</a><br />\n(用ethercalc 係想保障返大家 ， 喺入面edit係唔洗登入，完全匿名)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d28295f095ca0f26a4bb32249ae490fb582a9b","tid":1219651,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:21:07.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661f56510d8522d6bd5da8c07b080c56b4711c80","tid":1219651,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:27:55.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\